 "data": "@startuml SecureChatArchitecture
skinparam rectangle {
 Shadowing false
 BorderColor Black
 RoundCorner 10
 BackgroundColor White
}

' Define Client container
rectangle \"Client\" as Client #ddeeff {
 rectangle \"Application Layer\" as C_App
 rectangle \"Protocol Layer\" as C_Proto
 rectangle \"Security Layer\n(RSA‑OAEP)\" as C_Sec
 rectangle \"Transport Layer\n(Framer)\" as C_Trans
}

' Define Server container
rectangle \"Server\" as Server #ffeedd {
 rectangle \"Transport Layer\n(Framer)\" as S_Trans
 rectangle \"Security Layer\n(RSA‑OAEP)\" as S_Sec
 rectangle \"Protocol Layer\" as S_Proto
 rectangle \"Application Layer\" as S_App
}

' Internal flow arrows (optional, for clarity)
C_App -down-> C_Proto : uses 
C_Proto -down-> C_Sec : wraps 
C_Sec -down-> C_Trans : encrypts 

' Cross‑box message flow
C_Trans --> S_Trans : “Framed Encrypted Message” 

' Server internal
S_Trans -down-> S_Sec : unwraps 
S_Sec -down-> S_Proto : decrypts 
S_Proto -down-> S_App : delivers 

@enduml
",
 "format": "svg"
